description:
The Micro/Nano Technology Center (MNTC) is a core facility at the the University of Louisville that is comprised of two laboratories.  The first is a class 100/1000 $30 million 10,000 ft2 cleanroom facility.  The second facility is the Huson Imaging & Characterization Laboratory.  The Center’s expertise resides in micro and nanotechnology, sensors, transducers, microelectromechanical systems (MEMS), advanced materials, biomedical devices, space, and governmental applications that supports a wide range of research initiated by faculty, academic institutions, start-ups, medium and large businesses around the country. 

The MNTC is part of the KY Multiscale Node which is a member of the National Nanotechnology Coordinated Infrastructure network.

description:
Modern Talking are Dieter Bohlen & Thomas Anders. Originally formed in 1984, they created some of the most popular dance/pop music of the 80's, selling 7 Double Platinum albums, 11 Platinum albums and 39 Gold albums across Europe. In 1998 Modern Talking re-launched themselves in Europe with their album "Back For Good" which achieved the biggest comeback ever witnessed in the history of pop music. The album remained at the top of the German charts for over 20 weeks and has been released in over 50 countries. In nearly all these countries it has received Platinum and even Double platinum status.

Im Herbst 1984 veröffentlichten Dieter Bohlen und Thomas Anders unter dem Namen Modern Talking" ihre erste gemeinsame Single "You're My Heart, You're My Soul". Was keiner erwartet hatte, geschah: Auf Anhieb gelang den beiden der Sprung auf Platz 1 der Hitparaden. Daß dies keine Eintagsfliege war, bewiesen sie mit ihrer zweiten Single "You Can Win If You Want" - wieder Platz 1. Und was bisher nur die Gruppe Sweet in Deutschland geschafft hatte, gelang Modern Talking: Die ersten 5 Singles erreichten alle Platz 1. Der Erfolg kannte keine Grenzen - in 17 Ländern der Welt wareb sie inden Hitparaden plaziert. Der unverwechselbare Bohlen-Sound - Dieter Bohlen schrieb und produzierte die Titel - eroberte die Welt. 11 mal Platin und 39 mal Gold für ihre LPs sprechen für sich. Modern Talking haben ein Stück Musik-geschichte geschrieben.

description:
Hi everyone I wanted to share a little about myself and why I’m here. Not long ago, I lost my job working in a call center when AI systems took over. It was a tough time for me, especially being close to retirement and suddenly without a steady income.
But instead of giving up, I decided to turn that same AI technology into an opportunity. Now, I use AI to help me write and shape songs. Most of the words and ideas come from my heart — from my life, my memories, and my experiences. I also play guitar, and many of the guitar parts you hear in these songs are my own recordings.
AI can create music, but it still needs the human touch. It’s my emotions, my stories, and my feelings that guide the AI.
This is my new job, and my hope is to build something meaningful here. AI might have taken my old job, but it gave me a new one through music.
Thank you for listening, supporting, and being part of this journey. Every view, like, and comment means more than you know.

MIKROTRON - a brand of SVS-Vistek GmbH

The MIKROTRON brand is internationally known in the machine vision market for small, particularly robust High-Speed cameras that are used in industrial and scientific applications as well as in sports, advertising and nature filming.

SVS-Vistek GmbH has exceptional know-how in industrial image processing as an innovative manufacturer of high-quality industrial CCD and CMOS cameras for more than 35 years. 
We develop and produce a wide range of standard cameras as well as cameras with the highest resolutions and highest speeds, above-average image quality and all relevant interfaces in our own clean rooms at our headquarters in Gilching near Munich: Quality Made in Germany! 
With subsidiaries in the USA and Japan as well as a large partner network, we can advise, support and serve customers of many markets worldwide.
